href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kid-kapichi">小子·卡皮奇</a>（Molotovs and Kid Kapichi）获得了广受欢迎和高辛烷值的支持套装之后，乐队以“没关系的bollocks”开始，这是性手枪的“阳光下的揭幕战”节假日，以证明为什么他们仍然是卡特（Carter）被誉为“一直以来最伟大的朋克乐队”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="阳光下的性手枪假期 @皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅2025年3月24日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zbjBvscwV28?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="性手枪“非常空缺” 24.3.25住在皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sXupqQr1Xog?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><figure id="attachment_3849158" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3849158" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3849158" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/SEX_PISTOLS_ROYAL_ALBERT_HALL_5_JohnStead.jpg" alt="性手枪与弗兰克·卡特（Frank Carter）在伦敦皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅（Royal Albert Hall）举行的《十几岁癌症信托基金会》（Teenage Cancer Trust Show）演出：2025年3月24日，星期一（John Stead/提供）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/SEX_PISTOLS_ROYAL_ALBERT_HALL_5_JohnStead.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/SEX_PISTOLS_ROYAL_ALBERT_HALL_5_JohnStead-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/SEX_PISTOLS_ROYAL_ALBERT_HALL_5_JohnStead-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/SEX_PISTOLS_ROYAL_ALBERT_HALL_5_JohnStead-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/SEX_PISTOLS_ROYAL_ALBERT_HALL_5_JohnStead-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/SEX_PISTOLS_ROYAL_ALBERT_HALL_